    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-10-31T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-10-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="342"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d342">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Plumb</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 16.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-10-31">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 31, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> Your despatch No. 11, of 9th instant, has been
                    received, and I am much gratified to learn of your arrival at your post of duty,
                    and the cordial manner in which you have been received by Mr. Lerdo de Tejada,
                    the minister for foreign affairs, on the occasion of the presentation of your
                    letter of credence.</p>
                <p>His just appreciation of the policy of the United States as expressed in the
                    conversation as reported by you on that occasion is very pleasing to this
                    government.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Edward L. Plumb,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
